---
<section class="py-24 bg-primary-950 text-white overflow-hidden relative">
  <!-- Subtle pattern background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(#ffffff_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:40px_40px]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16">
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-24 h-24 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-gold-600"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-gold-600"></div>
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1450101499163-c8848c66ca85?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=2070" 
            alt="Firma de documento" 
            class="rounded-sm shadow-2xl grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gold-400 mb-4">Nuestra Identidad</h2>
        <p class="text-4xl font-serif font-medium leading-tight mb-8">
          Compromiso con la ética, <br class="hidden sm:block"/> la discreción y la confianza.
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gold-600/10 border border-gold-600/30 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-gold-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-2">Transparencia Total</h4>
              <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
                Informamos cada paso del proceso y los costos asociados de manera clara y directa desde el primer contacto.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gold-600/10 border border-gold-600/30 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-gold-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-2">Agilidad y Rapidez</h4>
              <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
                Entendemos el valor de su tiempo. Optimizamos nuestros trámites para brindar respuestas en plazos mínimos.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gold-600/10 border border-gold-600/30 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-gold-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-2">Personalización</h4>
              <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
                Cada cliente recibe un trato exclusivo y una solución a medida según la complejidad de su situación legal.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
